{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7ba0f2f36e","title":"周恩来接见广西两派时谈北京政法学院《政法公社》","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d0a7c95ff6","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":23,"articleId":"7ba0f2f36e"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"9da523fb00","name":"广西文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ac34e9c154","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见广西两派时谈北京政法学院《政法公社》","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ba0f2f36e"},{"id":"0b86de77cf","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ba0f2f36e"},{"id":"983dfab8fe","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二十三日零时15分至2时30分，周总理在人民大会堂接见了广西两派代表团部分代表。当谈到《政法公社》时，周总理指出：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ba0f2f36e"},{"id":"522ef1770e","type":"paragraph","text":"“政法学院有个陈荣金，起初大家都支持他。你知道他到处煽动，反对中央，反对中央文革小组，太猖狂了。”","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ba0f2f36e"},{"id":"353acf0977","type":"paragraph","text":"《联指》代表插话：“这家伙到处去夺权，他们还到广西同另一个组织结合夺公安厅的权。”","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ba0f2f36e"},{"id":"2dd4cc4ad4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹同志说：“政法公社就是到处去夺权。”","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ba0f2f36e"},{"id":"b76e3f8807","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理接着说：“我们现在已把他（指反革命分子陈荣金──编者）拘留了，”","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ba0f2f36e"}],"page":{"id":"dd80e419db","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"7ba0f2f36e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}